comment: 37259. ArcStart 55 (last present in patch 1817, name was probably never included)

37265. ArcStart 65 (last present in patch 1931); Toxic Mastermind; An Accord fugitive with incredible knowledge of aranha biology has escaped into the frontier surrounding Shanty Town. With the help of some local rebels the fugitive is developing biological weapons from aranha toxin. Help the Accord disrupt the weapon's development.

37288. ArcStart 69 (last present in patch 1931); Chosen Tech; Yuki Lin of Kisuton would like to take advantage of her current position and extract some valuable Chosen gear and technology from the region.

37287. ArcStart 66 (last present in patch 1931); Charge on Delivery; A courier for Vic the Crow has been waylaid en route with a much desired data package. Learn the status of the courier, then ensure Vic gets his goods.
